<HistoricalDocument xmlns="http://example.com/historicaldocument">
  <Metadata>
    <Language>German</Language>
    <WritingDirection>ltr</WritingDirection>
    <PhysicalDescription>Parchment, single folio side, good condition.</PhysicalDescription>
    <Description>List of names, possibly from a register or inventory.</Description>
    <Script>Latin</Script>
  </Metadata>
  <Page>
    <Header>
      <PageNumber>90</PageNumber>
    </Header>
    <Body>
      <List type="unordered">
        <Item>
          <Line>Heinrich von Külstetten</Line>
        </Item>
        <Item>
          <Line>ein barfues</Line>
        </Item>
        <Item>
          <Line>Conradus der schriben</Line>
        </Item>
        <Item>
          <Line>ob dem stift von</Line>
          <Line>mentz</Line>
        </Item>
        <Item>
          <Line>Hans Loſli camētar ze mentz</Line>
        </Item>
        <Item>
          <Line>ſant Johans ordens</Line>
        </Item>
        <Item>
          <Line>Heinrich von wiſſerode</Line>
          <Line>ritt</Line>
        </Item>
        <Item>
          <Line>Heinrich ſmit ſin knecht</Line>
        </Item>
        <Item>
          <Line>von Bern ob</Line>
          <Line>ochtländ</Line>
        </Item>
        <Item>
          <Line>ludwig von Dieſbach</Line>
        </Item>
        <Item>
          <Line>Hans von der gruͦben</Line>
        </Item>
        <Item>
          <Line>Hans Vlman</Line>
        </Item>
      </List>
    </Body>
  </Page>
</HistoricalDocument>
